des: City Weather is your dedicated source for real-time weather updates in Pune city. Whether you want to plan your day, stay informed, or simply satisfy your curiosity about the local weather conditions, our skill is here to help. Just ask Alexa, "What's the weather today?" and receive immediate weather details, including temperature and wind speed, for our city. It's the simplest way to keep up with local weather conditions. Try it now!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
